snippet.title: Marauder Game Open Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Marauder is now available to back through the fig open access program here: https://www.fig.co/campaigns/marauder  
   
Marauder is a multiplayer space pirate game set in an alternate history around the 1990s. Featuring space combat and realistic first person action.
